ime he might have could be devoted to learning. If you should find such a boy, let me know, for here there are only rascals to be got, and I am very much in need of someone to keep the house. Nothing more. I am well, thank God, and working hard. On the fifth day of November.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"1a336023-f874-41df-88a3-112b4843953b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":0,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"86d60343-4825-4241-9bdf-cd689e6dec81","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":20,"end":22,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","text":"yo","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"ebe73f0f-807c-4218-bef5-5b6995e2dc84","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":51,"end":53,"value":"66077dcf-3674-48a2-be09-76b3553dae5d","text":"la","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"54f34bbb-929d-4339-845b-b41fdf994051","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":73,"end":80,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","text":"Florenc","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"114c16a5-c3cb-4d76-be75-01559583a8ae","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":181,"end":182,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"m","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"b7c6a981-813e-4048-a4ad-66a49eeaaeb4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":185,"end":185,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"0bfd9f2c-3437-4d16-93fd-d8caa6b97503","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":199,"end":201,"value":"66077dcf-3674-48a2-be09-76b3553dae5d","text":"hi","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"a5338b7f-85af-4baa-8176-82a8b0c066ed","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":316,"end":317,"value":"66077dcf-3674-48a2-be09-76b3553dae5d","text":"h","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"238f5b81-abf3-467c-adc5-0b42f0fc103d","type":"codex/entity-refe